# Responsive Landing Page

This is a fully responsive landing page with an interactive navigation menu.

## Features
- Fixed navigation bar
- Scroll-based color change
- Responsive design for mobile & desktop
- Clean UI with hero, about, services, and contact sections

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## How to Use
1. Clone the repository
2. Open `index.html` in your browser
3. Customize text, colors, and images as needed

## Author
Developed by [Dipesh girase]
